&lt;br&gt;
Windowed, in which a window around PacMan con=
stitutes the inputs.&lt;br&gt;
Each tile in the window (except under PacMan himse=
lf) has an input&lt;br&gt;
associated with dots/walls, power pellets, and ghosts.=
 Users can&lt;br&gt;
select which inputs are used through the parameters file.&lt;br=
&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
Global, in which details of the maze are used as inputs, e.g.,&lt;br&gt;
P=
acMan&#39;s X and Y coordinates, ghost X and Y coordinates, ghost state,&lt;br&gt;
po=
wer pellet state, presence of walls or dots around PacMan. Again,&lt;br&gt;
